page.title: 17A Warwick Youth Club.
page.content: All Saints Youth Club is a club for people under 14,but you must be 8 to join. At the youth club they have lots of different games including snooker,table tennis and netball.Sometimes we have discos to raise money for the club fund.We also go ice skating at Solihull ice rink. Every week we have a news letter that tells you what is going happen in the next few weeks.The youth club is held every week at the Contact Centre in Warwick.We also have a room for Breakdancers.We have two computers and lots of games.Sometimes we have film shows also to raise money for the youth club funds.To join it costs 50p but from then its 35p for one evening a week.In the youth club there is a tuck shop run by members who get 20p worth of sweets ,free,for helping.
